<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="enormous-adj">enormous <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ɪ'nɔːməs/    美 /ɪ'nɔːrməs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>巨大的；庞大的</strong></h4>
<p>extremely large (huge)：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>an <strong>enormous amount</strong> of time / money 
大量的时间/金钱</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He knows so much about the subject. His knowledge is enormous. 
他对这门学科懂得很多，他的知识极其渊博。</p><footer>外研⑦ – 7</footer></div></div>